OL,6,FA woman from Brixham fears her
OL,7,Fterminally ill 93-year-old mother
OL,8,Fcould become the 'first fatality' of
OL,9,Fthe town's contaminated water crisis
OL,10,Fif she gets infected.JKaren Taylor
OL,11,Fcares for her mum, Audrey, and for the
OL,12,Fpast month has been painstakingly
OL,13,Fensuring she does not drink tap water
OL,14,Fwhich may still contain traces of
OL,15,Fcryptosporidium.JSouth West Water has
OL,16,Flifted the 'boil water' notice for
OL,17,Fsome people - but more than 2,000
OL,18,Fhouseholds are still in the warning
OL,19,Farea.
