OL,3,CWoman fears terminally ill mum could
OL,4,Cbecome 'first fatality' of water crisis
OL,6,FKaren told ITV West Country several of
OL,7,Fher neighbours have been hospitalised
OL,8,Fand she fears for her mum's health if
OL,9,Fshe becomes ill.
OL,11,F"She's four stone, she's fragile,
OL,12,Fthere's no way mum is well enough to
OL,13,Fbe taken to hospital," she said.
