OL,3,CWoman fears terminally ill mum could
OL,4,Cbecome 'first fatality' of water crisis
OL,6,F"It doesn't bear thinking about. She's
OL,7,Fbeen through a lot at 93. She doesn't
OL,8,Feven want to go yet. We're grateful
OL,9,Ffor the time that we've got but it
OL,10,Fwould be an injustice wouldn't it?
OL,11,FKaren and her family live in the
OL,12,FHillhead area of Brixham, very close
OL,13,Fto the source of a bacteria outbreak
OL,14,Fwhich has affected thousands of homes.
OL,16,FMore than a month on, they are still
OL,17,Fbeing told their tap water is not safe
OL,18,Fto drink.
