OL,3,CWoman fears terminally ill mum could
OL,4,Cbecome 'first fatality' of water crisis
OL,6,FSeveral of their neighbours have been
OL,7,Fadmitted to hospital with sickness.
OL,8,FKaren fears that if her mum became
OL,9,Fill, she would not survive.J"She
OL,10,Fwouldn't stand a chance," she said.
OL,11,F"I've been terrified of infecting her
OL,12,Fwhen I was infected and didn't know I
OL,13,Fwas infected.
OL,15,F"We didn't see this sneaking into the
OL,16,Fhouse. With Covid, we knew it was
OL,17,Fthere, but not this. It's heart-
OL,18,Frendering, worrying if I could pass it
OL,19,Fon to her because she would be their
OL,20,Ffirst fatality. She really would."
