OL,6,FLaura Flowerdew, South West Water's
OL,7,Fchief customer and digital officer,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We want to thank our customers,
OL,9,Fvisitors and local businesses for
OL,10,Ftheir continued patience while our
OL,11,Fteams work hard to clean the network
OL,12,Fand put interventions in place to
OL,13,Fprevent this from happening again.
