OL,3,CWoman fears terminally ill mum could
OL,4,Cbecome 'first fatality' of water crisis
OL,6,F"We are pleased to be able to remove
OL,7,Fthe boil water notice for 21 customers
OL,8,Falong the Hillhead to Boohay main. We
OL,9,Fwant to reassure everyone that we have
OL,10,Ftaken all the necessary steps,
OL,11,Fincluding rigorous sampling, to be
OL,12,Fsure their water is safe to use as
OL,13,Fnormal.
OL,15,F"We are working around the clock to
OL,16,Flift the boil water notice for the
OL,17,Fremaining customers in the Hillhead,
OL,18,FUpper Brixham and Kingswear area.
